{"tid":2091852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍到發黑] 你地有冇遇過啲咁嘅人？","createTime":"2020-07-03T01:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T06:15:29.000Z","uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30297e52745a53248c73fe7c74e4042508aec7fa","tid":2091852,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:56:25.000Z","msg":"無論係你身邊嘅人，或網上對話嘅人，你閑話家常，話佢知頭先喺街見到個癲佬，形容吓啲行為俾佢聽，佢二話不說就&quot;都唔夠啲黃絲廢青癲，打人燒嘢&quot;.......然後就大噴一輪<br />\n<br />\n你講今日好塞車，佢又嚟料：都已經算係咁，之前黑暴搞到成條路唔用得添.....<br />\n<br />\n你同佢傾不如叫外賣，佢話出街食啦，之前就話黃絲堵路冇啖好食姐，宜家冇事啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢乜鳩話題都搵機會扯去呢樣嘢，我先唔討論立場，因為立場係二元對立冇得變，但佢地個腦有冇第二樣嘢佔據？網上就懷疑佢係五毛要開工，但現實世界真係見過呢種人，同前幾年乜都佔中佔中咁，係咪被植入咗鬥爭洗腦mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca1e2519f63511b5f06d0ef40819ad64a13d580","tid":2091852,"uid":204539,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:01:42.000Z","msg":"已經睇大公文匯屈妓睇到壞咗腦<br />\n不如間唔時撚吓佢仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48dd9d80d68ed9b9f0d68b366bb9ad03ec5b1d10","tid":2091852,"uid":108006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"yahoo新聞下底啲評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\non9到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ccd2c3ae6391a837c36b5443a6e4651503aa2f","tid":2091852,"uid":104833,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍絲係咁上下水平"},{"pid":"bf21eb0789ef375d4b7eee2c8c12a8262bb81567","tid":2091852,"uid":30384,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"屋企個廢老就黎痾屎唔出都話廢青造成佢心情抑鬱痾唔出屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6d5d21868f2971ef3a4219ed5a5c